import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-home', templateUrl: './home.component.html', styleUrls: ['./home.component.css'] }) export class HomeComponent { constructor(private router: Router){} lessons(){ this.router.navigate(['members','lessons']); } }

Learn Japanese in Urdu, Hindi & Tamil!

Unlock the beauty of Japanese language from your home. Start mastering now!"

Why Choose Us?...

we believe in making learning Japanese accessible to all the Indians in Urdu, Hindi and Tamil. We offer affordable courses, allowing learners to study comfortably at their own pace, anytime, anywhere. "

What We Offer

Learn From Home

Start commute free learning

Affordable Price

Stop paying heavy fees

Life Time Access

Get rid of the scheduled classes

Overcome The Time Constraints

Statistics shows that many individuals are unable to complete the courses due to time constraints and their busy schedules. Our solution? We offer you life time access to our courses.

No More Commutation Issues

Commuting to a language institute can be unpleasant due to many reasons like road traffic and weather conditions. Our solution? We bring the institute to your doorstep, ensuring convenience and comfort for your language learning journey. "

Affordable Courses: Satisfy Your Appetite for Knowledge"

High pricing often deters many individuals from joining courses. Our solution? Affordable courses priced at the equivalent of a single day's meal.
